This paper deals with secret sharing and cryptography, which are core topics in computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of trusted third parties and protocols for communication, which are relevant to information theory (cs.IT) and cyber security (cs.CY). The paper also presents a protocol for law enforcement agencies to access sensitive information, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures (cs.DS).
